{"tid":199547,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《樹大招風》Trivisa 復活節假期重新上映","createTime":"2017-04-13T09:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T02:43:45.000Z","uid":4260,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51e9ff3c1f3a500ca29a1b997addcf52532f9d54","tid":199547,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"樹大招風將於4月14-17日復活節期間載譽歸來，記得趁機會入戲院睇我哋呢套最佳電影啦。<br />\n<br />\n其中兩位「最佳導演」#許學文 、 #黃偉傑 將會出席以下四場放映環節，與觀眾在映後分享！<br />\n<br />\n有問題問嘅朋友，記得買飛入場支持，到時問問佢地喇！<br />\n<br />\n上映戲院有：<br />\nFestival Grand Cinema @又一城<br />\n14/4: 3院 5:30pm<br />\n15/4: 3院 6:05pm<br />\n<br />\nMCL cinema @將軍澳新都城<br />\n14/4 6院: 3:00pm<br />\n15/4 6院: 3:00pm<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2psE55Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2psE55Q&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=a49d55f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2psE55Q</a>"},{"pid":"c10ef17ed87928ee6afd7797582fc7172115c952","tid":199547,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T09:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/fr/cp0/e15/q65/17854755_10156163865814498_2780226164538083639_o.jpg?efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;oh=842f69abdfdd681f6716e89f2688ef96&amp;oe=59547F5F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F17854755_10156163865814498_2780226164538083639_o.jpg%3Fefg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26oh%3D842f69abdfdd681f6716e89f2688ef96%26oe%3D59547F5F&h=f5219246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ZsE97uwjkEo&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZsE97uwjkEo%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=4ae699fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ZsE97uwjkEo&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"066cb14fefa5e3b67fbb399c1586615ac6cad06b","tid":199547,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"第三十六屆香港電影金像獎頒獎禮已於四月九日舉行，當最佳女主角惠英紅的得獎作《幸運是我》獲英皇發行安排於明天起重映之時。本屆奪得五項香港電影金像獎獎項、由寰亞發行的《樹大招風》亦將於復活節期間重映。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《樹大招風》於今屆香港影金像獎一共奪得五個主要獎項，當中包括了最佳電影，導演許學文、歐文傑與黃偉傑奪得最佳導演，龍文康、麥天樞與伍奇偉膺最佳編劇，林家棟更憑電影獲得最佳男主角，而梁展綸與David Richardson則獲得最佳剪接。電影以三位頭號通緝犯的故事為題，由三位導演各負責一名賊王，再由剪接將三個故事混在一起。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，寰亞電影方面已安排於四月十四日至四月十七日復活節假期期間，於九龍塘Festival Grand與港鐵寶琳站MCL新都城重映。倘若去年未有機會入場的觀眾，就要好好把握機會重溫這部金像獎得獎電影了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/55237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F55237&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=02721315\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/55237</a>"},{"pid":"d7850f5d4d6292de3a6f2ee82dd3117dd66b6a52","tid":199547,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f536f01911b33f04b1b08a28addafcbd8759104d","tid":199547,"uid":24944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:55:26.000Z","msg":"係咪終於可以收過千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8063c5895fc1f6b872c8b178d58e0e75464c9756","tid":199547,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32285d2517ac48e3da70931da184ee9196c97be5","tid":199547,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪終於可以收過千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好難講，場次又少，時間又西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face